---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Unterst&uuml;tzen - GonoPBX" description="Unterst&uuml;tze GonoPBX mit einem Kaffee oder hilf auf andere Weise. Open Source lebt von der Community.">

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="GonoPBX Logo" />
      </a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Menu">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M3 12h18M3 6h18M3 18h18" />
        </svg>
      </button>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="/#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#screenshots">Screenshots</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#techstack">Technologie</a></li>
        <li><a href="/release-notes">Release Notes</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/">Blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="/kontakt">Kontakt</a></li>
        <li><a href="/unterstuetzen">Unterst&uuml;tzen</a></li>        <li class="nav-lang">
          <a href="/" class="lang-link active">DE</a>
          <span class="lang-sep">|</span>
          <a href="/en/unterstuetzen" class="lang-link">EN</a>
        </li>

        <li><a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx" class="nav-cta">GitHub</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="support-hero">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:20px;">&#9749;</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px;">GonoPBX unterst&uuml;tzen</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.15rem;color:#4a5568;line-height:1.7;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
        GonoPBX ist ein Open-Source-Freizeitprojekt &ndash; komplett kostenlos und werbefrei.
        Hinter dem Projekt steckt ein einzelner Entwickler, der in seiner Freizeit an Features,
        Bugfixes und Dokumentation arbeitet.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Warum unterst&uuml;tzen -->
  <section style="padding:64px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <h2 class="support-page-h2">Warum unterst&uuml;tzen?</h2>
      <p style="color:#4a5568;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:24px;">
        Open-Source-Software entsteht nicht von alleine. GonoPBX verursacht laufende Kosten
        und erfordert viele Stunden Entwicklungsarbeit. Jeder Beitrag hilft, das Projekt
        langfristig am Leben zu halten.
      </p>
      <div class="support-costs-grid">
        <div class="support-cost-item">
          <span class="support-cost-icon">&#127760;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Domain &amp; Hosting</strong>
            <p>Server f&uuml;r Demo-Instanz, Website und Dokumentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="support-cost-item">
          <span class="support-cost-icon">&#128187;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Entwicklung</strong>
            <p>Neue Features, Bugfixes, Tests und Code-Reviews.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="support-cost-item">
          <span class="support-cost-icon">&#128218;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Dokumentation</strong>
            <p>Handbuch, Blog-Artikel, Release Notes und Anleitungen.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="support-cost-item">
          <span class="support-cost-icon">&#128736;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Infrastruktur</strong>
            <p>CI/CD, Docker-Images, SSL-Zertifikate und Monitoring.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tier-Karten -->
  <section style="padding:64px 0;background:#f7fafc;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;" class="support-tiers-section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;text-align:center;">
      <h2 class="support-page-h2">Mit einem Kaffee unterst&uuml;tzen</h2>
      <p style="color:#718096;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:1.05rem;">
        Jeder Beitrag &ndash; egal wie klein &ndash; ist eine gro&szlig;e Motivation.
      </p>
      <div class="support-tier-grid">
        <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/ankaios" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-tier-card">
          <span class="support-tier-emoji">&#9749;</span>
          <span class="support-tier-name">Kaffee</span>
          <span class="support-tier-price">5 &euro;</span>
          <span class="support-tier-desc">Ein Dankesch&ouml;n f&uuml;r die Arbeit</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/ankaios" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-tier-card support-tier-highlight">
          <span class="support-tier-emoji">&#11088;</span>
          <span class="support-tier-name">Supporter</span>
          <span class="support-tier-price">10 &euro;</span>
          <span class="support-tier-desc">Hosting &amp; Domain f&uuml;r einen Monat</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/ankaios" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-tier-card">
          <span class="support-tier-emoji">&#128640;</span>
          <span class="support-tier-name">Super-Fan</span>
          <span class="support-tier-price">25 &euro;</span>
          <span class="support-tier-desc">Treibt die Entwicklung richtig voran</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Andere Wege -->
  <section style="padding:64px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <h2 class="support-page-h2" style="text-align:center;">Andere Wege zu helfen</h2>
      <p style="color:#718096;text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:1.05rem;">
        Nicht nur Geld z&auml;hlt &ndash; es gibt viele M&ouml;glichkeiten, GonoPBX zu unterst&uuml;tzen.
      </p>
      <div class="support-ways-grid">
        <a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-way-card">
          <div class="support-way-icon" style="background:#fffaf0;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#dd6b20" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>GitHub Star</h3>
          <p>Ein Stern auf GitHub erh&ouml;ht die Sichtbarkeit des Projekts.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-way-card">
          <div class="support-way-icon" style="background:#fff5f5;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#e53e3e" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Bugs melden</h3>
          <p>Fehler gefunden? Ein Issue hilft, GonoPBX besser zu machen.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-way-card">
          <div class="support-way-icon" style="background:#f0fff4;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38a169" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ideen teilen</h3>
          <p>Feature-Vorschl&auml;ge und Feedback in den GitHub Discussions.</p>
        </a>
        <div class="support-way-card">
          <div class="support-way-icon" style="background:#ebf8ff;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3182ce" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 12v8a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-8"/><polyline points="16 6 12 2 8 6"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Weiterempfehlen</h3>
          <p>Erz&auml;hl Kollegen und Freunden von GonoPBX.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <ul class="footer-links">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://demo.gonopbx.de">Live-Demo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/unterstuetzen">Unterst&uuml;tzen</a></li>
        <li><a href="/impressum">Impressum</a></li>
        <li><a href="/datenschutz">Datenschutz</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Norbert Hengsteler. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Scripts -->
  <script>
    document.getElementById('navToggle')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.getElementById('navLinks')?.classList.toggle('open');
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-links a').forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', () => {
        document.getElementById('navLinks')?.classList.remove('open');
      });
    });
  </script>

</Layout>

<style>
  .support-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ebf8ff 0%, #fffaf0 50%, #f0fff4 100%);
  }

  .support-page-h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1a202c;
  }

  .support-costs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .support-cost-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .support-cost-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .support-cost-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .support-cost-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #718096;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .support-ways-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .support-way-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .support-way-card:hover {
    border-color: #bee3f8;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(49,130,206,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    color: inherit;
  }

  .support-way-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .support-way-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: #1a202c;
  }

  .support-way-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #718096;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .support-hero { padding: 48px 0 32px; }
    .support-hero h1 { font-size: 1.8rem !important; }
    .support-costs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .support-ways-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Dark mode */
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #0f172a 100%);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-hero h1 {
    color: #f1f5f9 !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-hero p {
    color: #94a3b8 !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-page-h2 {
    color: #f1f5f9;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-cost-item {
    background: #1e293b;
    border-color: #334155;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-cost-item strong {
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-cost-item p {
    color: #94a3b8;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-tiers-section {
    background: #1e293b !important;
    border-color: #334155 !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-way-card {
    background: #1e293b;
    border-color: #334155;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-way-card:hover {
    border-color: #475569;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-way-card h3 {
    color: #f1f5f9;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-way-card p {
    color: #94a3b8;
  }
</style>
